      <div class="realpost"><div>
        <blockquote class="thequote">You cannot travel anonymously. (Remember when we would mock Soviet-style “show me your papers” societies? That we’ve become inured to the very practice is a harm.)</blockquote>
        &mdash;<a href="https://www.schneier.com/blog/archives/2012/03/harms_of_post-9.html">Schneier on Security: Harms of Post-9/11 Airline Security</a>
      </div></div>
